        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Energy Sovereignty Act</b></p> <p>This bill repeals the requirement that states must revise implementation plans to prevent or eliminate air pollution endangering public health or welfare in other countries when directed to do so by the Environmental Protection Agency.</p>]]></text>
